{"id":28,"parent_id":7,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":28,"title":"1 Nephi 21","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 21"],[".studySummary",["i","The Messiah will be a light to the Gentiles and will free the prisoners—Israel will be gathered with power in the last days—Kings will be their nursing fathers—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49"},"Isaiah 49"],". About 588–570",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.1","order":"05.12.021.2597"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"And"],"again: Hearken, O ye house of Israel, all ye that are broken off and are driven out because of the wickedness of the pastors of my people; yea, all ye that are broken off, that are scattered abroad, who are of my people, O house of Israel. Listen, O",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"isles"],", unto me, and hearken ye people from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"far"],"; the Lord hath called me from the womb; from the bowels of my mother hath he made mention of my name."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.2","order":"05.12.021.2598"},["b","2"],"And he hath made my mouth like a sharp sword; in the shadow of his hand hath he hid me, and made me a polished shaft; in his quiver hath he hid me;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.3","order":"05.12.021.2599"},["b","3"],"And said unto me: Thou art my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"servant"],", O Israel, in whom I will be glorified."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.4","order":"05.12.021.2600"},["b","4"],"Then I said, I have labored in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"vain"],", I have spent my strength for naught and in vain; surely my judgment is with the Lord, and my work with my God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.5","order":"05.12.021.2601"},["b","5"],"And now, saith the Lord—that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"formed"],"me from the womb that I should be his servant, to bring Jacob again to him—though Israel be not gathered, yet shall I be glorious in the eyes of the Lord, and my God shall be my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.6","order":"05.12.021.2602"},["b","6"],"And he said: It is a light thing that thou shouldst be my servant to raise up the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"tribes"],"of Jacob, and to restore the preserved of Israel. I will also give thee for a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"light"],"to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"Gentiles"],", that thou mayest be my salvation unto the ends of the earth."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.7","order":"05.12.021.2603"},["b","7"],"Thus saith the Lord, the Redeemer of Israel, his Holy One, to him whom man despiseth, to him whom the nations abhorreth, to servant of rulers: Kings shall see and arise, princes also shall worship, because of the Lord that is faithful."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.8","order":"05.12.021.2604"},["b","8"],"Thus saith the Lord: In an acceptable time have I heard thee, O isles of the sea, and in a day of salvation have I helped thee; and I will preserve thee, and give thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"my servant"],"for a covenant of the people, to establish the earth, to cause to inherit the desolate heritages;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.9","order":"05.12.021.2605"},["b","9"],"That thou mayest say to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"prisoners"],": Go forth; to them that sit in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"darkness"],": Show yourselves. They shall feed in the ways, and their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"pastures"],"shall be in all high places."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.10","order":"05.12.021.2606"},["b","10"],"They shall not hunger nor thirst, neither shall the heat nor the sun smite them; for he that hath mercy on them shall lead them, even by the springs of water shall he guide them."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.11","order":"05.12.021.2607"},["b","11"],"And I will make all my mountains a way, and my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"highways"],"shall be exalted."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.12","order":"05.12.021.2608"},["b","12"],"And then, O house of Israel, behold,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"these"],"shall come from far; and lo, these from the north and from the west; and these from the land of Sinim."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.13","order":"05.12.021.2609"},["b","13"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Sing"],", O heavens; and be joyful, O earth; for the feet of those who are in the east shall be established; and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"break forth"],"into singing, O mountains; for they shall be smitten no more; for the Lord hath comforted his people, and will have mercy upon his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"afflicted"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.14","order":"05.12.021.2610"},["b","14"],"But, behold, Zion hath said: The Lord hath forsaken me, and my Lord hath forgotten me—but he will show that he hath not."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.15","order":"05.12.021.2611"},["b","15"],"For can a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"woman"],"forget her sucking child, that she should not have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"compassion"],"on the son of her womb? Yea, they may",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"forget"],", yet will I not forget thee, O house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.16","order":"05.12.021.2612"},["b","16"],"Behold, I have graven thee upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"palms"],"of my hands; thy walls are continually before me."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.17","order":"05.12.021.2613"},["b","17"],"Thy children shall make haste against thy destroyers; and they that made thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"waste"],"shall go forth of thee."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.18","order":"05.12.021.2614"},["b","18"],"Lift up thine eyes round about and behold; all these",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"gather"],"themselves together, and they shall come to thee. And as I live, saith the Lord, thou shalt surely clothe thee with them all, as with an ornament, and bind them on even as a bride."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.19","order":"05.12.021.2615"},["b","19"],"For thy waste and thy desolate places, and the land of thy destruction, shall even now be too narrow by reason of the inhabitants; and they that swallowed thee up shall be far away."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.20","order":"05.12.021.2616"},["b","20"],"The children whom thou shalt have, after thou hast lost the first, shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"again"],"in thine ears say: The place is too strait for me; give place to me that I may dwell."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.21","order":"05.12.021.2617"},["b","21"],"Then shalt thou say in thine heart: Who hath begotten me these, seeing I have lost my children, and am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"desolate"],", a captive, and removing to and fro? And who hath brought up these? Behold, I was left alone; these, where have they been?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.22","order":"05.12.021.2618"},["b","22"],"Thus saith the Lord God: Behold, I will lift up mine hand to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Gentiles"],", and set up my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"standard"],"to the people; and they shall bring thy sons in their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"arms"],", and thy daughters shall be carried upon their shoulders."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.23","order":"05.12.021.2619"},["b","23"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"kings"],"shall be thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"nursing fathers"],", and their queens thy nursing mothers; they shall bow down to thee with their face towards the earth, and lick up the dust of thy feet; and thou shalt know that I am the Lord; for they shall not be ashamed that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"wait"],"for me."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.24","order":"05.12.021.2620"},["b","24"],"For shall the prey be taken from the mighty, or the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"lawful captives"],"delivered?"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.25","order":"05.12.021.2621"},["b","25"],"But thus saith the Lord, even the captives of the mighty shall be taken away, and the prey of the terrible shall be delivered; for I will contend with him that contendeth with thee, and I will save thy children."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.26","order":"05.12.021.2622"},["b","26"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"feed"],"them that oppress thee with their own flesh; they shall be drunken with their own blood as with sweet wine; and all flesh shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"know"],"that I, the Lord, am thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"Savior"],"and thy Redeemer, the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_26d"},"Mighty One"],"of Jacob."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.1a","order":"05.12.021.2623"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.1.1-26"},"Isa. 49:1 (1–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.1b","order":"05.12.021.2625"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.4"},"1 Ne. 22:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.21.20-22"},"2 Ne. 10:21 (20–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.1c","order":"05.12.021.2627"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.1"},"D&C 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.3a","order":"05.12.021.2629"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/25.55"},"Lev. 25:55"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/41.8"},"Isa. 41:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.46.45-46"},"D&C 93:46 (45–46)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.4a","order":"05.12.021.2631"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/55.2.1-2"},"Isa. 55:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.5a","order":"05.12.021.2633"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.24"},"Isa. 44:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.5b","order":"05.12.021.2635"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.6a","order":"05.12.021.2637"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Twelve Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.6b","order":"05.12.021.2639"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.5"},"Ezek. 5:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.9.8-9"},"D&C 103:9 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.11.6-11"},"Abr. 2:11 (6–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.6c","order":"05.12.021.2641"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.11"},"3 Ne. 21:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.8a","order":"05.12.021.2643"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.11.6-15"},"2 Ne. 3:11 (6–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.11.8-11"},"3 Ne. 21:11 (8–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.16.16,25"},"Morm. 8:16 (16, 25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.9a","order":"05.12.021.2645"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-for-the-dead"},"TG Salvation for the Dead"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-in-prison"},"Spirits in Prison"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.9b","order":"05.12.021.2647"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5"},"2 Ne. 3:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.9c","order":"05.12.021.2649"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.14"},"Ezek. 34:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.25"},"1 Ne. 22:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.11a","order":"05.12.021.2651"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/62.10"},"Isa. 62:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.27.23-32"},"D&C 133:27 (23–32)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.12a","order":"05.12.021.2653"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/43.5.5-7"},"Isa. 43:5 (5–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.13a","order":"05.12.021.2655"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.23"},"Isa. 44:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.13b","order":"05.12.021.2657"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.13c","order":"05.12.021.2659"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/22.28"},"2 Sam. 22:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.27"},"Ps. 18:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.13"},"Isa. 49:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.15a","order":"05.12.021.2661"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.15b","order":"05.12.021.2663"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/103.13"},"Ps. 103:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.15c","order":"05.12.021.2665"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/17.38"},"2 Kgs. 17:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/41.17.15-17"},"Isa. 41:17 (15–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.8"},"Alma 46:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/61.36"},"D&C 61:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.2"},"133:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.16a","order":"05.12.021.2667"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/13.6"},"Zech. 13:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.17a","order":"05.12.021.2669"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.13.12-20"},"3 Ne. 21:13 (12–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.18a","order":"05.12.021.2671"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.11.11-13"},"Micah 4:11 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.20a","order":"05.12.021.2673"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.21a","order":"05.12.021.2675"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.1"},"Isa. 54:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.27"},"Gal. 4:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.22a","order":"05.12.021.2677"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19.18-20"},"Isa. 66:19 (18–20)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.22b","order":"05.12.021.2679"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.12.10-12"},"Isa. 11:12 (10–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/18.3"},"18:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/9.16"},"Zech. 9:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.22c","order":"05.12.021.2681"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.8"},"1 Ne. 22:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.8.8-9"},"2 Ne. 10:8 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.23a","order":"05.12.021.2683"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.16.14-16"},"Isa. 60:16 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.23b","order":"05.12.021.2685"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.6"},"1 Ne. 22:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.23c","order":"05.12.021.2687"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.18"},"Gen. 49:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/27.18"},"Prov. 27:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.13"},"2 Ne. 6:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.2"},"D&C 98:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.11.10-11,45"},"133:11 (10–11, 45)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.24a","order":"05.12.021.2689"},["b","24a"],["span.small","IE"],"the covenant people of the Lord. See also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.25"},"v. 25"],".",["span.small","JST"],"Isa. 49:25 reads: “But thus saith the Lord; even the captives of the mighty shall be taken away, and the prey of the terrible shall be delivered;",["i","for the mighty God shall deliver his covenant people"],"…”"],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.26a","order":"05.12.021.2691"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.17.15-17"},"1 Ne. 14:17 (15–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.13.13-14"},"22:13 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.14.14-18"},"2 Ne. 6:14 (14–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.26b","order":"05.12.021.2693"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/26.6"},"Ezek. 26:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.22.20-22"},"Mosiah 11:22 (20–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.26c","order":"05.12.021.2695"},["b","26c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-savior"},"TG Jesus Christ, Savior"],"."],["div",{"id":"26d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.26d","order":"05.12.021.2697"},["b","26d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],"."]]}
